Terminal type is now 'qt'

gnuplot> set parametric

	dummy variable is t for curves, u/v for surfaces
gnuplot> set trange [0 to 2*pi]
gnuplot> set xrange [-1 to 1]
gnuplot> set yrange [-1 to 1]
gnuplot> plot sin(t),cos(t)

